# A form of [[physical]] [[punishment]] in which a [[beating]] is applied to the [[buttocks]], or an incident of such punishment.

===Adjective===
'''spanking'''

#{{colloquial}} An intensifier in the phrase ''brand spanking new'' to indicate absolutely most recent.
#Fast and energetic, as in ''a spanking pace''.
#(particularly in nautical usage) Brisk and fresh, as in ''a spanking breeze'.'
#A general intensifier (now rare except in ''spanking new'') as in ''a spanking good time''.
#remarkable of its kind.

